@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tazyjo(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.56
    v0 = tmp
    tmp = (0.70 - ((tmp + 0.61 - v1 + 0.19) / v1))
    v1 = (v1 + ((v1 + 0.68 - v1 + 0.48) / wp.cos(tmp + 0.78)))
    data[tid] = v0
